entry.title: PhilHealth funds used like 'blank checks' by some hospitals: lawmaker

media:group.media:title: PhilHealth funds used like 'blank checks' by some hospitals: lawmaker
media:group.media:description: The state health insurer parked funds in some hospitals that were "way bigger" than what they needed for coronavirus patients, allowing the money to be used like "a blank check", a lawmaker said Friday.
